<%# Generates a survey reminder page to send to a user%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      This email is a reminder that Santa Clara University is seeking your feedback for [insert class] in an online survey. Your responses will help us to improve this lab. Please click on the link below to access the survey: <%= link_to 'Respond to your survey', :controller => 'surveys', :action => 'edit', :id => @survey.id, :queryKey => @survey.key %>
    </p>
    <p>
      THE SURVEY PERIOD ENDS [insert date] at midnight. Once a survey has been submitted, it cannot be accessed again. If you do NOT complete a survey for one or more of your lab, your ability to view current term grades WILL BE DELAYED by a week. Your response to the survey is completely anonymous and cannot be traced to you. A summary of results of surveys of all classes will be available on SCU's website after grades have been submitted.
    </p>
    <p>
      ---------------------------------------------------
    </p>
    <p>
      Note: Please do not respond to this email; it has been created automatically. If you have any questions, please contact evalmgr@scu.edu or call 554-4006. Thank you.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>